Responsibilities:

  Assist in analyse of workforce hiring and retrenchment trendsm workforce skills requirements and employability needs
  Assist in data collation, extraction, analyses and visualisation of data/statistics/information
  Collate data/statistics/information for regular internal and external reports
  Engage companies and provide basic manpower related advise
  The incumbent may be required to implement digital marketing and other relevant marketing related activities

Other information:

  The duration of the traineeship is 6 months
